{
  "stem": "490.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And when we walked in the morning, we saw on the snow-- the snow was still full of blood, which they told us this was the, the, the blood of people-- of elderly people who could not walk as fast or that didn't walk in the line the way they want them to-- so they just shot them in the middle of the road.",
      "word_count": 64
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And they-- so we followed-- we saw the snow and the blood, full of, of Jewish blood.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "It was stepped on.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] [BACKGROUND NOISE] And so we stayed in this block or two, it was, for another while.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And then they finally built a concentration camp, a-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] outside this factory where we worked, with barbed wire, with electric barbed wire.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And they put some barracks.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And one day, they didn't allows us to go back to the city at all.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And we were held there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "We put on, you know, we were-- had to live there from this day on.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "It was probably in 1941, which we stayed, we remained in these barracks, watched by the Ukrainians, which they helped the Germans, more than the Poles, even.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it was the Ostrowiec, [POLISH], the Ostrowiec.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It, it actually, it was a working, a labor camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it was watched by electric wire and the Ukrainians.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was in walking distance to the factory where we worked.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And sometimes, they even brought in from the other camps, they brought in people to-- because they needed more workers in this, in this camp-- in this factory.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I would say-- well, it was all kinds of people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "First of all, in this camp, in the beginning, there were only the people that worked in this factory.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
